name: Miss Found - Demo
description:
In 1923 in New York City a young girl went missing and the police contracted the private detective Addison Cannon from the agency "Miss Found" to solve the case. It´s their last chance to rescue their career after multiple failed cases.

A short level of a Hidden Object Game created in only one month by the team Happy Guaventree in their 2nd Semester, 2020.
